11:05.998 --> 11:07.306
Hello.

11:10.202 --> 11:11.374
Hey.

12:03.389 --> 12:05.027
Where's my drink?

12:22.575 --> 12:24.020
(SPEAKING FRENCH)

12:27.113 --> 12:28.456
I don't smoke.

12:29.014 --> 12:30.891
But you do speak French.

12:33.986 --> 12:35.329
