a Mexican death wish.

12:50.870 --> 12:52.315
You traveling alone?

12:52.805 --> 12:54.307
What business
is it to you?

12:56.142 --> 12:57.678
None, really.

12:58.377 --> 13:01.824
But from what I saw
in there, I thought
we could make ourselves

13:01.881 --> 13:03.656
