Don't draw attention.

16:11.804 --> 16:13.215
Who's there?

16:14.473 --> 16:15.884
Over here.

16:19.878 --> 16:21.186
Where am I?

16:23.282 --> 16:24.522
Hell.

16:27.486 --> 16:29.090
(SHUTTER OPENING)

16:29.254 --> 16:31.757
THE EXECUTIONER:
What is the one thing
we all have in common?

16:32.992 --> 16:34.266
Death.

16:34.660 --> 16:39.075
The only questions are
how and when
the Grim Reaper will visit.

16:40.265 --> 16:43.007
A problem you need not
worry about any longer.

16:47.239 --> 16:48.843
This point forward,

16:49.141 --> 16:51.121
your life isn't yours anymore.

16:51.877 --> 16:53.322
It belongs to me.

16:54.346 --> 16:56.326
You are no longer David Lord.

16:56.515 --> 16:58.392
He ceases to exist.

16:59.385 --> 17:02.298
Your name is Death Dealer.

17:03.088 --> 17:04.532
You were bred to fight.

17:05.257 --> 17:06.327
To kill.

17:06.692 --> 17:08.194
And to die.

17:08.260 --> 17:09.829
Who are you?

17:09.895 --> 17:12.034
Do what you were born
to do, Death Dealer,

17:12.431 --> 17:14.911
and your demise
will be one of glory.

17:15.501 --> 17:17.377
Resist,

17:17.435 --> 17:19.415
and I promise you pain
in the likes of which

17:19.471 --> 17:22.247
you never could
conceive imaginable.

17:22.907 --> 17:24.546
What do you want?

17:26.779 --> 17:28.554
Help! Hello?

17:29.448 --> 17:31.189
Somebody help me!

17:31.250 --> 17:32.456
Let me out!

17:32.951 --> 17:34.294
(ALARM BLARING)

17:42.461 --> 17:43.462
(BUZZING)

17:49.068 --> 17:50.479
Your name is Death Dealer.

17:50.536 --> 17:52.106
What are you doing?

17:52.171 --> 17:53.411
You were bred to fight.

17:54.239 --> 17:55.912
To kill. To die.

17:56.375 --> 17:59.913
(ECHOING)
Your name is Death Dealer.
You were bred to fight.

17:59.978 --> 18:02.015
Kill. Death Dealer.
To die. To kill.

18:02.081 --> 18:04.891
Your name is Death Dealer.
You were bred to fight.

18:04.950 --> 18:07.396
