18:34.513 --> 18:36.254
(DISTORTED NOISES)

18:40.018 --> 18:41.258
(SCREAMS)

19:07.613 --> 19:08.614
(MOANS)

19:14.253 --> 19:17.063
So, what do we
know about him?

19:17.623 --> 19:19.034
He's a fireman
from Denver.

19:19.258 --> 19:20.737
I thought he was a doctor.

19:20.792 --> 19:23.466
He has a
paramedic license.
He's not a doctor.

19:23.529 --> 19:24.599
Family?

19:24.696 --> 19:26.607
Wife, deceased.

19:26.665 --> 19:28.770
KADEN: He's a fucking doctor.

19:29.334 --> 19:32.406
At least the last guy
she grabbed was
a competitive kendo artist.

19:32.471 --> 19:34.883
Well, this guy is
a fireman, okay?

19:34.940 --> 19:39.047
Have you seen him?
He's, like, 85 kilograms.

19:39.111 --> 19:40.181
186...
Milla.

19:43.315 --> 19:44.419
He'll fight.

19:44.483 --> 19:46.554
He's fucking useless.
He's a piece of shit.

19:47.486 --> 19:48.897
It's so typical
of you, Milla.

19:48.954 --> 19:50.262
My dear Kaden.

19:50.322 --> 19:51.995
He's been in your
care for three days

19:52.057 --> 19:53.695
and he's yet to give
you the time of day.

19:55.327 --> 19:59.070
Maybe Kaden's
tired old shtick
won't break him.

20:00.032 --> 20:02.842
