my responsibility.

20:09.541 --> 20:13.990
May I remind both of you
they are all my fighters.

20:14.046 --> 20:15.457
And this is my world.

20:16.548 --> 20:17.925
But you're
absolutely right, Milla.

20:18.684 --> 20:19.719
It's your risk.

20:20.185 --> 20:21.493
It's also your ass.

20:22.521 --> 20:24.660
Well, he’ll fight
and he'll win.

20:28.126 --> 20:29.400
Do whatever it takes.

20:29.861 --> 20:31.135
Just make sure he fights.

21:35.827 --> 21:37.170
DAVID: What's your name?

21:37.829 --> 21:40.833
TAIGA: You want
my real name or
the one they gave me?

21:41.533 --> 21:42.603
