22:09.928 --> 22:11.999
We're going to die here,
David Lord.

22:12.264 --> 22:14.437
Nah, nah,
don't talk like that.

22:14.900 --> 22:17.005
My wife, Akiko,

22:18.770 --> 22:20.909
