But I'm not. I'm weak.

22:27.446 --> 22:28.447
I'm tired.

22:29.815 --> 22:31.158
And I'm angry.

22:31.216 --> 22:33.526
And all I went to do
is kill those motherfuckers!

22:35.020 --> 22:36.863
Showtime.

22:43.295 --> 22:44.638
(GRUNTING)

22:48.734 --> 22:49.872
(SCREAMING)

22:51.970 --> 22:54.382
Hold your breath! Hold!

22:56.375 --> 22:57.718
Tough it up!
Tough it up!

23:03.281 --> 23:04.521
(CHOKING)

23:07.886 --> 23:09.126
(LAUGHS)

23:27.506 --> 23:28.780
(GREETING IN FRENCH)

23:31.443 --> 23:32.581
(GRUNTS)

23:36.848 --> 23:38.623
You look like shit.

23:40.185 --> 23:43.223
The magic cocktail
is already
whispering in your ear.

23:43.889 --> 23:45.129
Why are you doing this?

23:45.624 --> 23:47.160
What's your name?

23:55.100 --> 23:56.670
David Lord.

23:58.637 --> 24:00.810
What were you going
to name your child?

24:00.872 --> 24:02.681
Leave my family
out of this.

24:02.741 --> 24:05.881
Your wife, she's pretty.

24:07.312 --> 24:09.451
Such a pity she's gone.

24:13.018 --> 24:16.966
In the Marines,
how many men, women
and children did you kill?

24:19.591 --> 24:21.070
No matter.

24:21.126 --> 24:23.197
'Cause you aren't prepared
for what's about to happen.

24:24.596 --> 24:27.076
Whether you live or die.

24:29.034 --> 24:31.036
How will you live or die?

24:33.038 --> 24:34.346
It's your choice.

24:36.908 --> 24:38.080
What?

24:39.978 --> 24:40.979
You want me?

24:41.046 --> 24:42.150
I'd love to get
my hands on you.

24:42.214 --> 24:43.852
That's the spirit.

24:52.657 --> 24:53.795
No, no, no, no!

24:54.392 --> 24:55.393
(BUZZING)

25:25.323 --> 25:26.358
(SPEAKING MANDARIN)

25:26.424 --> 25:28.870
New guy doesn't
stand a chance.

25:30.228 --> 25:31.400
