25:32.163 --> 25:35.167
We need to talk
about your TPS reports.

25:35.500 --> 25:38.310
Yeah. The cover sheets.

25:39.204 --> 25:40.740
I know. I know.

25:54.252 --> 25:57.529
Ahh. Home again, home again.

25:58.490 --> 26:00.868
And how are my two
beauties this fine day?

26:01.860 --> 26:03.237
Ready to go.
Ready to go.

26:03.295 --> 26:04.706
Magnificent.

26:04.763 --> 26:06.436
Let's make something
special, shall we?

26:11.469 --> 26:13.073
THE EXECUTIONER:
What is your name?

26:14.406 --> 26:16.147
David Lord.

26:22.714 --> 26:26.753
No. Your name is
Death Dealer.

26:27.586 --> 26:28.963
Now I'm gonna
ask you again.

26:30.088 --> 26:34.537
What is your name?

26:39.898 --> 26:41.377
Input a six-second delay.

26:42.567 --> 26:44.137
Link the video screen.

26:45.403 --> 26:46.882
Ladies, if you will.

26:47.672 --> 26:49.083
Lights.

26:52.744 --> 26:54.121
Lay in graphics.

26:56.448 --> 26:58.291
Marvelous!

26:58.950 --> 27:02.762
Outstanding.
You've outdone yourselves,
my little pearls.

27:03.121 --> 27:08.969
We are going live
in three, two, one.
Cue music.

27:15.433 --> 27:16.741
(MUSIC PLAYING)

27:43.228 --> 27:45.469
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
I'm not gonna fight!

27:49.134 --> 27:50.670
Boring.

28:01.646 --> 28:02.647
(GRUNTING)

28:20.865 --> 28:21.866
(SPEAKING MANDARIN)

28:21.933 --> 28:22.934
What a coward.

28:23.068 --> 28:26.072
If I was a betting man,
Milla, and I am,

28:26.137 --> 28:28.640
I'd say you're
going to lose this one.

28:45.223 --> 28:47.134
CRAIG: Oh, no.
Get up, get up, get up!

28:50.895 --> 28:52.499
Ladies, please,
do something.

28:52.564 --> 28:54.566
