I'm falling asleep here.

29:25.563 --> 29:26.598
CRAIG: Yeah!

29:26.664 --> 29:27.665
RICK: Oh, dude.

29:30.735 --> 29:31.736
(SPEAKING MANDARIN)

29:31.836 --> 29:33.247
He's shit.

29:34.305 --> 29:35.306
What?

29:44.549 --> 29:45.550
(SCREAMS)

29:45.617 --> 29:48.188
Oh! Well, I'll be damned.

29:48.586 --> 29:50.088
