the Fan-atics to vote.

30:04.836 --> 30:06.281
Survey says...

30:08.039 --> 30:11.282
Mr. Executioner,
come on down!

30:11.442 --> 30:14.286
I'm a paramedic.
I'm gonna stop the bleeding.

30:16.915 --> 30:18.019
What's he doing?

30:18.216 --> 30:20.025
I've got a child.

30:24.455 --> 30:26.230
