30:30.995 --> 30:33.771
Can you smell it?
It's just like sweetness.

30:34.065 --> 30:35.408
Naughty boy.

30:35.567 --> 30:37.308
Get him out of there, please.

30:46.277 --> 30:52.228
And we are out
in three, two, one.

30:53.418 --> 30:57.867
Brilliant!
Absolutely brilliant show.

30:57.922 --> 31:01.699
You were marvelous.
And you were marvelous.

31:14.372 --> 31:15.851
THE EXECUTIONER: Hey!

31:15.907 --> 31:17.818
Stop right there!

31:19.010 --> 31:21.286
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
What are you doing?

31:21.346 --> 31:24.054
He's an embarrassment.
I should have cut him
In half there and then.

31:24.115 --> 31:25.617
No, no, no, no!

31:25.683 --> 31:28.425
You are not going
to kill him!

31:28.486 --> 31:29.692
Yes, I am.

31:29.754 --> 31:32.132
Kaden, be reasonable.

31:34.893 --> 31:37.305
Reasonable?
This cunt deserves to die.

31:37.362 --> 31:39.501
Yes he does,
but not this way.

31:39.831 --> 31:41.572
It's wasted
if he dies off camera.

31:41.633 --> 31:42.668
Fuck the cameras!

31:42.967 --> 31:44.742
Kaden, where's your
sense of adventure?

31:46.271 --> 31:47.409
He wronged me.

31:47.472 --> 31:49.918
He wronged us!

31:49.974 --> 31:53.922
Look, I want to hold his head
on the chopping block for you.

